{"id": "zakelijke-dienstverlening-leunt-zwaar-op-amerikaanse-markt-en-technologie__c4-paragraph__0024", "text": "Business Services is the lubricant of the Dutch knowledge economy. New ways of working are often the first to be applied in this sector, making it an important driver in the transition to a circular economy.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "zakelijke-dienstverlening-leunt-zwaar-op-amerikaanse-markt-en-technologie__c4-paragraph__0024", "source_slug": "zakelijke-dienstverlening-leunt-zwaar-op-amerikaanse-markt-en-technologie", "source_title": "Business services rely heavily on the American market and technology", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/sectoren-en-trends/sectorprognoses/zakelijke-dienstverlening/zakelijke-dienstverlening-leunt-zwaar-op-amerikaanse-markt-en-technologie.html", "source_date": "2025-06-19", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "sectorprognoses", "topic": "sectoren en trends", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 24, "n_chunks_total": 29, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
